reviewText: It was hard to find, and I want because of the good reviews I read. It is good... I like it!

Hello
  I am writing to say how much I love Latin Cardio , My girlfriend and I do it whenever there are classes available but sometimes we cant make it to the class so we purchased this DVD and its just as fun doing it at home as it is doing it in the gym. I recommend this dvd to anyone who wants to get into shape but still wants to have LOTS of fun doing it. I give it 5 stars any day.
